                                     "SwapLineIf", "IfTimeIs",                                                
                                        "Day",  "Stepping into the third floor of Adventure Apartments, you are faced with a long hallway with doors on one side, and impressively sized windows on the other that let in the bright sunlight. The glassy panes offer a panoramic view of the plaza, where you can see people milling about and a variety of billboards displaying six advertisements for all kinds of succubus beauty products.",
