                                "NameOfScene": "Look out of the panoramic windows.",
                                "theScene": [  
                                            "SwapLineIf", "IfTimeIs",                                                
                                                "Day", "You can see six advertisements for all kinds of succubus beauty products and assorted paraphernalia hanging from some of the distant buildings, their garish colors and attention-grabbing graphics standing out even in the middle of the colorful Capital.",
                                                "Night", "You can see seven advertisements for all kinds of succubus beauty products and assorted paraphernalia hanging from some of the distant buildings, the sparkling bright glow of their backlit surfaces standing out starkly in the dark of the night.",
                                            "EndLoop",
                                            "SwapLineIf", "IfTimeIs",
                                                "Day", "The offers on display feature the following deals: 'Fresh Succubus Milk at 306 St! Order now!' 'Impeccable Makeup for only 999 Eros!', 'Buy 69 packs of lipstick and get the 70th free!', 'Night Bane: 100% energy, 0% natural ingredients!', 'Your ad here for 605 Eros!',  and '310 different flavors of ice cream!'",
                                                "Night", "The offers on display feature the following deals: '10th anniversary celebratory sale!', 'Go {i}Badatata!{/i} with {i}777{/i}, the Midnight Bunny Casino-brand golden lipstick!', 'Deals so good they might as well be five-finger discounts!', 'Always remember to knock thrice!', '8% discount on three brands of sunglasses!', '9 out of 10 dentists recommend Mintclear toothpaste!', and 'Enjoy the luxury of our four-star makeup.'",
                                            "EndLoop",
                                            "SwapLineIf", "IfTimeIs",                                                
                                                "Day", "Aside from this show of aggressive marketing, you can also make out silhouetted figures walking to and fro across the plaza, the diminutive shapes minding their own business as they go about their day. Lastly, the occasional decorative tree breaks up the utilitarian monotony of stone pathways and the omnipresent dark-and-neon Ars Delusian color scheme, giving some rather welcome rest to your eyes.",
                                                "Night", "Aside from this show of aggressive marketing, the city is strangely still and the plaza below is utterly vacant of people, giving a surreal feeling to the urban vista.",
